    "path": "/v1/exchange_rates",
    "tag": "default",
    "summary": "List all exchange rates",
    "description": "\u003cp\u003e[Deprecated] The \u003ccode\u003eExchangeRate\u003c/code\u003e APIs are deprecated. Please use the \u003ca href=\"https://docs.stripe.com/payments/currencies/localize-prices/fx-quotes-api\"\u003eFX Quotes API\u003c/a\u003e instead.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eReturns a list of objects that contain the rates at which foreign currencies are converted to one another. Only shows the currencies for which Stripe supports.\u003c/p\u003e",
