    "path": "/v1/invoices/{invoice}/update_lines",
    "tag": "default",
    "summary": "Bulk update invoice line items",
    "description": "\u003cp\u003eUpdates multiple line items on an invoice. This is only possible when an invoice is still a draft.\u003c/p\u003e",
